        <div class="msgSubject">Damage, Support, and Control</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-22 08:06:24 | Edited: Nov 22 2010  8:08am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290434784190042710" id="quote-1290434784190042710" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290434784190042710" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=223&amp;mid=1290434784190042710&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290434784190042710&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290434784190042710" onclick="followToggle('add','1290434784190042710')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
